table_caption: Main effect of serum NfL on DTI metrics in MC.
table_foot: Unstandardized regression coefficient B and adjusted p-values for serum NfL from a series of linear mixed effect models in each ROI, which included random intercepts for family, and fixed effects for age, sex, and NfL. Dependent variables were the average WM metrics (FA, MD, DA, and DR) from each ROI. N = 117. WM = White matter; NfL = Neurofilament light chain; ROI = region of interest; SE = standard error.
